
# Azure Dashboard Guide

## Basic Usage
- Access the Azure Dashboard from the Azure Portal home page
- The dashboard is a customizable workspace to monitor resources
- Pin frequently used resources and metrics for quick access

1. Default Dashboard
- Start with the default dashboard to learn basic layout
- Contains system health, resource usage, and cost information

2. Customization
- Click "Edit" to modify dashboard
- Drag and drop tiles to rearrange
- Resize tiles by dragging corners
- Add new tiles via "Add tile" button

